271
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:41,470
Why did you do that?! I told that you I can't get married so soon after Franz died!

272
00:18:41,570 --> 00:18:42,730
That's all right.

273
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:43,540
Father!

274
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,270
Shut your mouth!

275
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:48,650
Are you saying that you don't care if l... no, this entire family...

276
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:51,970
...dies penniless in a ditch somewhere thanks to your self-centeredness?!

277
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,910
Father, calm down.

278
00:18:54,050 --> 00:18:56,780
Calm down?!
How am I supposed to calm down?!

279
00:18:57,420 --> 00:19:01,120
My stocks have taken a nosedive! They aren't worth the paper they're printed on now!

280
00:19:01,260 --> 00:19:04,720
Give up on this worthless piano nonsense of yours!

281
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:07,730
You're not serious...

282
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:10,860
You're the only one who can save this family.

283
00:19:11,270 --> 00:19:14,640
You've got to marry Andrea right away!

284
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:17,370
But what about my feelings?

285
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:18,910
They don't matter.

286
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:22,450
All that matters to me is that I get my money back.

287
00:19:26,390 --> 00:19:30,290
Thanks to this, Andrea's fortune will be mine!

288
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:36,820
Eugenie, at this moment, you're the most precious thing in the world to me.

289
00:19:51,850 --> 00:19:54,870
Franz is still here with us.

290
00:19:56,080 --> 00:19:57,740
That's the way
I see it.

291
00:19:58,890 --> 00:20:02,650
I get the feeling that he's showing us what path we have to take.

292
00:20:14,700 --> 00:20:16,000
Renaud...

293
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:34,840
And where might you be going at this late hour?

294
00:20:47,300 --> 00:20:49,270
No! Stop it!

295
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,860
Let go!

296
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:53,370
No!

297
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:00,740
No!

298
00:21:02,820 --> 00:21:07,780
Even the daughter of an aristocrat would be ruined for life if something like this is done to her, wouldn't she?

299
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:09,520
Wouldn't she?!

300
00:21:12,330 --> 00:21:15,390
The day after tomorrow, you're going to belong to me.

301
00:21:16,360 --> 00:21:20,200
The main course will have to wait until then...

302
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:26,960
Albert, save me...

303
00:21:29,140 --> 00:21:30,400
Albert!

304
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:57,690
I'm not the man I used to be

305
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:08,410
And what you see is not what it seems

306
00:22:08,490 --> 00:22:15,000
I traveled through space to be with you here

307
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:23,630
What you don't know, you shouldn't fear

308
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:31,850
You won't see me coming...

